               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of Dīvān by Ilāhāhbādī, Muḥammad Afẓal</summary>
                  <msItem class="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/subjects/sh2010105559" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1069-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>A commentary, here without title, on the 
                <title key="work_22914">Dīvān</title>of 
                <persName xml:lang="per-Latn-x-lc" key="viaf_56731778" role="ant">Ḥāfiz̤</persName>by Muḥammad Afẓal Ilāhābādī (d. 1124/1713). According to another copy of this work, IO Islamic 2482 (Ethé 1270), this is part of a larger work entitled 
                <title key="work_22914">Kashf al-astār ʻan vujūh  mushkilāt al-ashʻār</title>consisting of 18 treatises on Persian poetry.
                        </p>
                        <p>13 lines to a page; nastaʻliq; dated 25 Zu al-Qaʻdah 1253 (20 February 1838).</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="person_n82692642">Ilāhāhbādī, Muḥammad Afẓal</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="person_n82692642">الله آبادی، محمد افظل</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_22914">Sharḥ-i Dīvān-i Ḥāfiz̤</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_22914">شرح دیوان حافظ</title>
                  </msItem>
